keyValuePair.Value: [PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] You must be disappointed with the result today?
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] After an agonising loss like that, are you disappointed at all in the performance today?
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER] [CALM - ALL] Our fans deserved better.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER] [CALM - ALL] We knew what we needed to do today but couldn't manage it. I just wish we could have given our amazing fans something to cheer for today,
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][SYMPATHIZE DEFENDERS] We did our best so I can't fault the players.
I can't say that I'm happy, but we did our best so I can't fault the players.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][SYMPATHIZE DEFENDERS] We've done well to get this far so I'm not too disappointed. We've consistently played well in this competition so overall I can't fault the lads.
We've done well to get this far so I'm not too disappointed. We've consistently played well in this competition so overall I can't fault the lads.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][CRITICIZE MIDFIELDERS] We've squandered a great opportunity.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][CRITICIZE MIDFIELDERS] It was our chance to get to the final and we missed it. Of course I am disappointed.
It was our chance to get to the final and we missed it. Of course I am disappointed.
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] A tough loss, what do you feel went wrong for your side today?
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] You needed just one more goal today but failed to make it happen. Did you hope for better from your team?
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][CRITICIZE DEFENDERS] To be honest yes, I expected more from them.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][CRITICIZE DEFENDERS] Considering what was at stake today, I really hoped for better from my players.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER] [CALM - ALL] I'm not going to comment on that.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER] [CALM - ALL] I have no desire to go over the details over and over. It's time for us to focus up on our next opponents.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][SYMPATHIZE ATTACKERS] I'm happy with the players' efforts.
I'm happy with the players' efforts.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][SYMPATHIZE ATTACKERS] To get so close and fail to win was frustrating, but we weren't that far from grinding out the result.
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] Is it a case of what might have been for your players tonight?
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] A close run thing but it's %1s who are celebrating. Is it a case of what might have been for your side?
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][SYMPATHIZE MIDFIELDERS] Yes, I thought we deserved more from the game.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][SYMPATHIZE MIDFIELDERS] I can agree with that, we were really unlucky not to progress from this tie.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER] [CALM - ALL] It's useless to debate now.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER] [CALM - ALL] The result's not going to change, so I'd prefer to focus on the future and how I can bring success to this great club.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][CRITICIZE ATTACKERS] In all honesty, no.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][CRITICIZE ATTACKERS] No, in fairness we didn't show enough quality to stay in %1s, we congratulate the opposition and we'll try and find a way to take that next step.
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] A tough loss to exit the competition, where do you feel it went wrong today?
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] An agonising loss sees your team exit the competition, what are your feelings after today's performance?
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][CRITICIZE DEFENDERS] We've only got ourselves to blame.

[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][CRITICIZE DEFENDERS] In the end we've only got ourselves to blame, we had chances to win the tie and to not do so is obviously disappointing, we'll move on and try to learn from this experience.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER] [CALM - ALL] Our fans deserved better.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER] [CALM - ALL] We needed another goal today but it just wouldn't go in. I wish we could have given our amazing fans something to cheer for today, but it wasn't to be.
[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][SYMPATHIZE ATTACKERS] I have my fair share of the blame to take.

[PLACEHOLDER ANSWER][SYMPATHIZE ATTACKERS] I really think we could have gone far in %1s. It's disappointing to go out the way we did but we'll come back stronger as a result. I'll take my share of the blame and I'll analyse where it went wrong for us.
